main event: A UFO sighting occurred at Waverly AFS, Iowa on February 29, 1961, where an object was detected on radar.
interesting points: The object was sighted on Mark X Radar at a distance of .345 x 10 miles, The sighting lasted for 10 minutes, The object disappeared 3.25 miles away at 0202, The courses reported were SW and NE, and it was suggested to be a balloon but was classified as unidentified.
